reviewText: Loved all of the stars and the skits on the show! In fact, loved it so much, I bought my brother one.
QUALITY ITEMS FROM A QUALITY SELLER! WOULDN'T HESITATE TO BUY FROM AGAIN! HIGHLY RECOMMENDED!!!
I like most of the shows on this DVD. Just who I like and don't like when it comes to the Country guest on the show! Still love it though!
I haven't followed cable TV for a long time, yet this was a fun series.

This two disc set was an absolute find for me.  Very inexpensive and with hours of great fun.  I'd rate this higher than the blue comedy tv series and way ahead of the Jeff Foxworthy show.  Great stand up , some wonderful musical stars, fun variety sketch comedy and loads of bonus content.  For a few bucks you get hours of laughs. Recommended.
Jeff Foxworthy is true to form. He works out clever comedy skit versions of the jokes that he has told for 20 or more years! AND he gets the BEST in country music entertainers.
